title: SCTV Network -- Melonville Elections
description:
SCTV Network -- Melonville Elections (11-19-1982) -- Guest starring David Rasche avi

David Rasche later became semi-famous as TV&#039;s "Sledge Hammer" in 1986. But as with everyone else on this show, it was at Second City on stage in the 1970s where he got his start. David plays a Councilman who runs against Libby Wolfson in this SCTV episode.

The music guest is gospel singer Linda Hopkins.
